   "source": [
    "# Bangla Handwritten Sentence Recognition OCR\n",
    "### Kaggle Training Notebook\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook trains a TrOCR-style model (ViT encoder + Transformer decoder) on the BN-HTRd dataset.\n",
    "Two tokenizer variants are compared: BPE vs BnGraphemizer (grapheme-level)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Clone Repository"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import os\n",
    "import sys\n",
    "\n",
    "REPO_URL = \"https://github.com/hasanimam72108/-bangla-handwritten-ocr\"\n",
    "REPO_DIR = \"/kaggle/working/bangla-handwritten-ocr\"\n",
    "\n",
    "if not os.path.exists(REPO_DIR):\n",
    "    !git clone {REPO_URL} {REPO_DIR}\n",
    "    \n",
    "os.chdir(REPO_DIR)\n",
    "sys.path.insert(0, REPO_DIR)\n",
    "print(f\"Working directory: {os.getcwd()}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Contents: {os.listdir('.')}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Install Dependencies"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
